h2 How this works
p
        div 1. Asks twitter for your list of friends
        div 2. Looks at your friends' bio and url to see if there is a Google+ profile or a gplus.to nickname
        div 3. Pings http://gplus.to trying to find any accounts matching your friends twitter names. eg glus.to/zdam
